    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, quick question. I'm flying into Heathrow and need to get up to Edinburgh. I was thinking about taking the Heathrow Express to Paddington then catching an LNER train from there, and maybe a bus at the end. How much buffer time should I realistically leave between the train transfers so I don't miss my connections if there's a delay?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
